# Force LF line endings for text files so oxfmt --check, vitest snapshots,
# and shell-script heredocs behave identically on Linux/macOS and Windows
# (where Git's default core.autocrlf would otherwise convert to CRLF on
# checkout). Listed assets are flagged binary so Git skips line-ending
# munging for them.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tgz binary
